      "id": 1000,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "# Xiaoguai — SLO Overview (DEC-022)\n\n4 SRE golden signals + 28-day error-budget tracker per SLO. Source of truth: [`docs/runbooks/slo.md`](https://github.com/zw008/xiaoguai/blob/main/docs/runbooks/slo.md). Architecture: DEC-022 (`xiaoguai-agent-design/docs/hld.md`) + LLD-OBS-001.\n\n`xiaoguai_slo_burn_rate{signal,window,surface,tenant}` is the live burn-rate gauge; recording rules under `slo-api-tier-*` provide the windowed SLI ratios shown in the time-series panels.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text",
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Latency — p95 SLI ratios + burn rate",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 6 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "xiaoguai:slo_api_lat_chat:ratio_rate1h",
          "legendFormat": "chat p95 ratio (1h)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Chat p95 SLI Ratio (1h)",
      "description": "ratio_rate1h on /v1/chat/* against 5 s threshold. 1.0 = at SLO, >1 = breaching.",
      "type": "stat"
    },
